  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of HL Tablet in Non-alcoholic Fatty Liver Disease Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 2 Study to Assess Safety and Efficacy of HL Tablet on Reducing Hepatic Fat in Non-alcoholic Fatty Liver Disease Patients</official_title>
