  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the safety and efficacy of HL tablet on reducing hepatic fat in
      non-alcoholic fatty liver disease patients. The patients are allocated to three groups; low
      dose, high dose, and placebo control group.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
